SUMMARY:Support Through the Pause
DESCRIPTION:Support Through the Pause is a monthly meetup and safe space to learn and share around the physical and emotional transitions of perimenopause and menopause. Facilitated by TNT member\, Helaina Altabef\, mental health counselor and certified coach. \nClick here to RSVP!
